Licensing[edit]

The flag of Åland is described in the Provincial act on the flag of Åland (Landskapslag angående landskapet Ålands flagga, ÅFS 41/1992). Thus it falls under

Public domainPublic domainfalsefalse
This file is in the public domain in Finland because it is a part of a decision or a statement issued by a public authority or other public body in Finland. Section 9 of the Finnish Copyright Act specifies that no copyright exists in such material. (Link to the Act)
